column5: Not much of a report here.....lost a nice bow first thing and seen 2 bows caught and there were a couple guys snaggin salmon....seen em snag 2 and take off.....so pretty slow today....oh well its gotta get hot sometime REAL soon...   Hawk
I heard from some guys today that Owen sound was hot yesterday and meaford as well. He mentioned one more place that's up there but forgot the name.
Sorry to hear about the nice bow you missed chickenhawk but at least you got out there and gave it your best shot Thanks for sharing Leechman
you were @ the maitland?  i was there all day. hooked into 3 bows lost them all... my buddy hooked 2 brought in one, around 7 pds... i saw atleast 10 caught @ the 21 bridge.
yeah we didnt go to that spot till about noonish...didn't see a fish caught all afternoon
